Ronnie and List Members,
    3 more clubs for you to add to the list.

Long Island Volkswagen Club
Has a newsletter, monthly meetings in 2 different locations on Long
Island, NY and can be checked out at  http://www.livc.net/

Long Island Bus Alliance
For owners of any year or generation of Bus.  Monthly meeting and an
e-mail list that can be joined by anyone who is interested.
http://groups.yahoo.com/group/busalliance/ is the address to sign up
for the list, then send a message introducing yourself and ask for
directions to the meetings if you'd like to attend.  No dues, no
membership forms, no newsletter.

NorthEastern Volkswagen Association   (N.E.V.A.)
Also on Long Island.  I don't much about the club, so check it out at
http://www.glenn-ring.com/neva/

